Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.41,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:20.22,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.20,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:22.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:27.28,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:34.22,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoyed anyway, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your thesis... half-done, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Another break from work, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nyugaku-iwai, the high school gift... you sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With your name on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... They'll find out sooner or later....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever hear of Seiran Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I've heard of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She was selected as a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that easy to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, to my surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was selected as a candidate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,3. Is Nanako Disqualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I collected some information about what the Sorority sisters dislike most.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls who cannot use keigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls who cannot dress and behave in a "classy" manner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially, girls who can't be punctual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it I can hear from so far away, ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the outsider who was chosen as a candidate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything special about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exceptionally pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she must be the only daughter of a very rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's lower middle-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. That makes no sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure it out either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a narrow stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't pass if you walk spread out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means, go on, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Nanako, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have used some kind of dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'd never have been selected as a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nasty upstart she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow she got chosen over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have some very sneaky way of cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be even more mortifying if she is chosen as a member!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok. She'll withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got the goods on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What "goods"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I found Nanako Misonoo's weakness. A truth she can't deny...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In my father's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there are many such secrets to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Your father is a famous lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd been born into the elite like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, the most elite of the elite...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How I hate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always some girl like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Feigning such innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who somehow steals what is rightfully mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, it's Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. I've been better. But I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Anything urgent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular. Just a meaningless good-night call,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a rumor runs its course in 75 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,75 more days, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, what did you decide to wear to the party tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still torn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Between a black dress and a bright red one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But yours has got to be pink. Especially powder pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. They look at us even colder today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dreading some sort of exam announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they have unscheduled exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it says...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We suspect there was cheating in the selection of the Sorority candidates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this cheating led to the selection of Nanako Misonoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have the looks and charm to qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, she's not really the daughter of Professor Misonoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an injustice that such a person be selected as a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko! Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This garbage belongs in a garbage can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's something about her almost like a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided not to go to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After such an incident... I just can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You were... defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is hate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is it finally painful enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how much you respect and love your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you're not his real daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I know how close you two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is torturing me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dirty thing they are doing to you, and an outrageous insult, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go to the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not going because of this would just increase the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be ashamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all! You are innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But damn. Not going was my final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the decision you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wonder why I was selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have selected you, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority members saw into your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been? I thought you might have gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say you won't attend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I confess... I must confess that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot happening and I've been thinking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When I decided to go, I somehow thought I might be accepted after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much confidence, nor any faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought, wouldn't it be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To see and experience the Big Sister's gorgeous life style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I realized that I am somewhat vain, frivolous, and a social butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite its perhaps being wrong, I'm still so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling is new to me... completely new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako? Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a phone call from Ichinomiya Fukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,From Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, about tomorrow's Soro... Soro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sorority, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Sorority party...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is changed to three o'clock. And she said "hello".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock? okay. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stunned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You really dressed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you're determined to make a perfect impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first things first! Please be so good as to kindly be seated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm stumped! That's you asked to meet me at twelve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the time for the Sorority party!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The time was changed! That's why we can meet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't bake a cake like I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we can eat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your treat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was {\i1}your{\i0} treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You said so on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll order... some angel cake, a lemon square,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and a New York cheese cake with blue berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What can Nanako be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san is the only one who hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could... Could I use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just getting sleepy when the sky got lighter and I heard the delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried shutting my eyes even harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sky just kept getting lighter and lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up and took a shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I thought I'd use the time for homework, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat at my desk but couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to talk like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is the Misonoo residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako has left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She has?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She did leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But something must have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She would never be this late without calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, everyone... Now we will start the interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When they hear their name called,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,each candidate should come into the interview room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Interviewers, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time! Time to go home and do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I finally feel a little relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Homework for me, party for you... What a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are selected...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Default, Shinobu Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you start ballet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was six, my mom took me to lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a part in a play in English in Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've had a tutor for English and French since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you may go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That finishes the last of the candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo hasn't arrived yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san? A very unfortunate case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The first rule for the Sorority is being on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet she is late by more than two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how she feels about being a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The party is over. So, let's wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Miya-sama! Please give her a little more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.81,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Seiran School, Seiran School.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shinobu-san is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this dress makes me look too girlish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, too late to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:22:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Udaishou Kaoru-no-Kimi in The Tale of Genji was born with a beautiful aura, like hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Her chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry! I didn't mean to stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ok, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to attend the Sorority party?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody left a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The party was finished a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! The party starts at three!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So calm you are. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All the freshmen have left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Sisters are so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:14.06,Opening,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:19.53,Opening,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:25.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:30.61,Opening,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:36.95,Opening,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:42.36,Opening,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:45.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:47.94,Opening,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.94,0:24:50.30,Opening,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:55.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.48,0:25:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being terribly late for the selection party,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.86,0:25:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako is nevertheless selected for membership.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Aya, rejected by the Sorority, starts a campaign of slander against Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.57,0:25:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...revealing the affair between her father, Professor Misonoo, and Nanako's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Music Box
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.06,0:25:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
